ENTRY            A1007   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
SUBENT        A1007001   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
BIB                  7         18
TITLE      Neutron production cross sections and energies for the
           reactions T(p,n)3He, D(d,n)3He, and T(d,n)4He.
AUTHOR     (H.Liskien,A.Paulsen)
REFERENCE  (J,ND/A,11,569,1973)
INSTITUTE  (2ZZZGEL)
ANALYSIS   This work presents recommendations based on data
           compilation of differential and integrated (with
           respect to the neutron observation angle) cross
           sections.
COMMENT    Data from other authors are normalized for evaluation
HISTORY    (19820504C) Compilation produced by Arzamas RFNC-VNIIEF
           (19961211A) Corrected REL-REF in Subent 011, 012
           (19970206U) Last checking has been done.
           (19990115U) CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases
           (20190716U) SD: METHOD deleted; ANALYSIS added.
           (20260208A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           The accuracy of data presentation has been revised
           according to the tables.
ENDBIB              18
